.sp
.LP
\fIDa followin sections is informative.\fP
.SH EXAMPLES
.SS Changin tha Current Owner of a File
.LP
Da followin example shows how tha fuck ta chizzle tha ballershizzle of tha symbolic
link named \fB/modules/pass1\fP ta tha user ID
associated wit "jones" n' tha crew ID associated wit "cnd".
.LP
Da numeric value fo' tha user ID is obtained by rockin tha \fIgetpwnam\fP()
